<DOCNO> LA113090-0029 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 315351 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 30, 1990, Friday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 2; Metro Desk 
</P>
