$100,000 each. They are: Chhiv Chhuon, 20, of the 4100 block of Euclid Avenue; 
Serey Siev, 19, of the 10,000 block of Westchester Avenue and Chan Um, 21, of 
Long Beach. 
</P>
<P>
The investigation is continuing and other arrests are expected, police said. 
