<TEXT>
<P>
Authorities are investigating the complaint of a 27-year-old Whittier woman who 
told deputies that she was sexually assaulted by a man dressed like a police 
officer and driving a four-door sedan painted black and white like a patrol 
car. 
</P>
<P>
However, no suspects have been arrested and a detective said authorities have 
been unable to contact the victim since the attack was reported. 
</P>
