consisting of three styles of solid-gold watches -- are of such luxury that 
they got a champagne reception at South Coast Plaza. ; Photo, Featured in 
Chanel's new Mademoiselle Collection are three watch styles of 18-karat gold 
and pearls. LACY ATKINS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
