<P>
SANTA FE TO SELL 730 MILES OF TRACK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
Chicago 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Santa Fe Railway will sell 730 miles of track in the Southwest to privately 
held Orient Railcorp. Terms of the deal were not disclosed. 
</P>
<P>
The three segments of track are in Oklahoma and Texas. 
</P>
